==Chinese==
===[[Mandarin]]===
[[Pinyin]]: wúlùnrúhé

===Idiom===
'''[[無論]][[如何]]'''

# in any case; at any rate; whatever happens; no matter what
#: '''''無論如何'''，[[我們]][[也]][[不能]][[對不起]][[朋友]]''
#: '''''No matter what''', we can not do anything that would cause embarassment to our friends''
#: ''[[今天]][[考試]]，[[你]]'''無論如何'''[[也]][[要]][[去]]''
#: '''''Whatever happens''', you must be there for today's test as well.''

===Alternate forms===
[[无论如何]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

